error: corsa not found

vize check requires '@typescript/native-preview' to be installed.

To install, run one of the following:

  npm install -D @typescript/native-preview  # npm
  pnpm add -D @typescript/native-preview  # pnpm
  yarn add -D @typescript/native-preview  # yarn
  bun add -D @typescript/native-preview  # bun
